Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three males!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to thoroughly inspect\Nthe area surrounding the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd wait for Detective Kratoky\Nto arrive and give us orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take full responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detain any suspicious people on sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What kind of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody who looks suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem taking\Norders from a new detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Suk of the Prague Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really nasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector... Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been savagely beaten to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:01:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left of his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he hadn't dropped his badge...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we probably wouldn't have known who, he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two more dead males over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them was shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other was beaten to death, just like the Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Preserve the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of people are suspicious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:13.59,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(434,0)\pos(360,362)}Detective Suk
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're making fun of me because\Nthey think I'm a newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those officers won't even listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is coming from someone who's unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You vomited at the scene, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants to take orders from\Nan agent who's that weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're fond of detective stories\Ndoesn't mean you're fit for the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan has always been capricious since our college days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how nicely the late\NInspector Zeman treated me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a newcomer who didn't know his right from his left...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Zeman taught me how to be a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I respected Inspector Zeman from\Nthe bottom of my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get revenge for Inspector Zeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find the killer, even if I have to do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get up early tomorrow for work, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason you guys can work with peace of mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is because I'm fighting for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, drink some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, we work for justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we get killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a thankless job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the girl from the supermarket...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, after my night shift, I go to the supermarket...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen her there twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to say something to her, but I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl as pretty as she is won't even look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Jan Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely not suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite my looks, I'm actually a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:05:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be scared just because I'm a detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off-duty right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is all private!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a futile effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess we'll lend him a hand today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry he's being so forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really depressed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind keeping him company?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss he admired was involved in an incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he's doing is moping around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who's moping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no good people like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be like Inspector Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm never going to forgive the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely catch him, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm just rambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to work hard to catch\Nthat person, for your inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've talked a lot about myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I haven't heard anything about you yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know my real name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whats that supposed to mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to guess who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} a detective, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave these kinds of things to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't know it myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way you could know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only things I know about myself are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cedok Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Three Frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When can I see you again...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?  It was useless after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as a dream, and give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've confirmed the identities of the two men\Nwho were killed with Inspector Zeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:55.58,Location,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(434,0)\pos(323,372)}Prague Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is Cestomil Malad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other is Jakov Shachek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were both ex-sergeants of the former\NCzechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the collapse of communism...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they took shady jobs in the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After examining the blood traces at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've discovered that some was not from\NInspector Zeman, Malad, or Shachek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood was type AB, Rh positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the amount of blood, it's likely that the\Nunidentified person was also seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently trying to identify that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you daydreaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We re here busting our asses because\Nof the loss of Zeman, that great man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that attitude of yours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said at the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the stories told by the witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a man walking around\Nthe area right after the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that he's tall and thin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and dressed like a traveler carrying\Na large bag on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put all your efforts into locating this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way... that she'd come again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found that killer yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm sitting in here like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that killer is out there, free...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day before he was killed, he spent\Nthe night investigating a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of case was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where an old man who ran an unlicensed orphanage...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his female assistant were both killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the following morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was questioning the first person\Nto discover the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first person to discover the crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed like a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he was tall and skinny...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was carrying around this heavy-looking bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Large bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where that man is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I think I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the station to look it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cedok Bridge...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the Three Frogs...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cedok Bridge is in the old urban Michalska area...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Frogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can meet that girl if I come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He checked out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:11:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Mr. Grimmer... Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer checked out two days ago, in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed Inspector Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was this Grimmer person who stayed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I realize it sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch him, Inspector Zeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk?! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask you the same question, Detective Patera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you got this far all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually hoping to take most of the\Ncredit for Inspector Zeman's case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're this far already, Detective\NPatera, then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll give credit where it's due.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd like to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but keep this case a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capturing Grimmer ASAP should be our...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This case is more complicated than it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know about the top secret investigation\NZeman was entrusted with, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Zeman... was on a top secret investigation...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was to root out all of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,former Czech secret police officers who\Nstill work at the Prague station...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hide themselves by altering their personal histories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former Czechoslovakian secret police...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two men who were killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were also former secret police, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the chief of police, myself, and\Na few others know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get in too deep, you might also get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then what should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Grimmer might show up at this hotel again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be on the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Suk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get yourself a girlfriend or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're daydreaming during meetings\Nand while sitting at your desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's not my girlfriend or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a girl... who comes to\Nthe bar I go to sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Introduce me to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not your girlfriend or anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk isn't coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are good-looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Suk's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Patera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said there was a really pretty girl at this bar so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on a stakeout tonight, so he can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little wouldn't hurt, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning Detective Janacek
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it from Mr. Patera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl you found is pretty hot, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to that bar, Mr. Patera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't do.anything to her, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Detective Patera is famous for being a player...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She completely ditched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be really hard to get if even\NMr. Patera couldn't seduce her, Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I was just... talking to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun enough for me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you muttering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Section Chief Farobek wanted you\Nto go to Inspector Zeman's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone gave me these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a whiskey bonbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that suspect who looks like a toothpick a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've emptied most of Inspector Zeman's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only his personal belongings are left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pack up all these things and take\Nthem to the Inspector's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a gym locker key.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many sweat-stained \N shirts and towels in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Files...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are detailed files of all the station\Nemployees and their personal histories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my profile is in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't know about the top secret investigation\NZeman was entrusted with, do you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was to root out all of the...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}former Czech secret police officers who\Nstill work at the Prague station...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and hide themselves by altering their personal histories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come only Detective Patera and\NDetective Janacek aren't in here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is an abnormal sum of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you deduce from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Zeman was investigating the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-As a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he learned that both Detective Patera and Detective\NJanacek were former Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is very unfortunate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Inspector Zeman accepted money...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to conceal the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a very alarming problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l-lt is very unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't speak to anyone about this case just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will contact you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to your regular duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is becoming a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a mistake by underestimating\Nsomeone as young as Suk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't solved the case of\Nthat toothpick killing Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now another problem shows up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go with money again, \N like we did with Zeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that doesn't work, there's only one thing left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to avoid causing myself any trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for letting,you both in, even though\NI knew of your personal histories!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully, we can hush everything up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure could use a drink right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some whiskey bonbons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got these from a very hot chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust anyone now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell me, if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that Inspector Zeman, of all\Npeople, would do something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in him, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only peace in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.99,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:44.42,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:44.42,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:47.38,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:23:01.06,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:23:01.06,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:25.92,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:34.34,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:36.80,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
